routines.name: Muscle Workout
routines.techniqueSummary:
* Be focused with each exercise 
* Try to beat your last result 
* Don't cheat and keep clean technique
routines.description: The Muscle Workout is designed to increase your general strength and to build muscles. You shouldn't only work on skills but also always on the basics fitting your level. It is all about the sets and reps!

routines.name: Leg Workout
routines.techniqueSummary:
* Be focused with each exercise 
* Try to beat your last result 
* Don't cheat and keep clean technique
routines.description: The Leg Workout is designed to increase your general strength and to build muscles in your lower body. Training the lower body is very important. It consists of big muscle which will generate a lot of testosterone. This will increase also the muscle growth in the whole body. You shouldn't only work on skills like the Pistol Squat, but also always on the basics fitting your level. It is all about the sets and reps!

routines.name: Planche/Front Lever
routines.techniqueSummary:
* Be focused with each exercise 
* Try to beat your last result 
* Don't cheat and keep clean technique
routines.description: This Workout hits the whole upper body and focuses on achieving the Planche and Front Lever. These two skills are complementary and can be trained together. The exercises alternate between the Planche progressions and Front Lever progressions in order to reduce the workout time while ensuring enough rest for each muscle group.

routines.name: Upper Body Circle
routines.techniqueSummary:
* Be focused with each exercise 
* Try to beat your last result 
* Don't cheat and keep clean technique
routines.description: The Upper Body Circle is a round based workout, which contains basic upper body exercises. The goal is to improve muscle endurance. Therefore keep always clean technique, but try to reduce rest time to a minimum and to complete the workout as quick as possible. The workout can nicely be added after Skill/Strength work to increase volume.
